          "w": "Note that هَؤُلَاءِ is mostly used with human beings. Its use to refer to non-human beings is rare.\n\n4. The plural of هُوَ is هُمْ. Unlike the singular هُوَ the plural هُمْ is used to refer only to human beings, e.g. "
